name: hyStik QuickMask 805 - Fast Painting Masking Tape
description: hyStik General Purpose Masking Tape 805 is ideal for bundling, packaging, binding, splicing, light duty temporary masking and other office, home, school or industrial applications. It can be applied to glass, aluminium, steel, wood, concrete, plaster, paper and plastic films.
